           APPLE_ID=you@email.com APPLE_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx ./scripts/build-and-notarize.sh

        3. Create signed release:
           GITHUB_REPO=Vladimirbabic/typebettermac ./scripts/create_release.sh

        4. Copy the <item> output and paste it below (newest first)

        5. Create GitHub Release:
           gh release create v1.1 Releases/TypeBetter-1.1.zip --title "v1.1" --notes "Release notes"

        6. Commit and push this appcast.xml
        -->

